sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant web_consumer as Web Consumer
    participant api_gateway as API Gateway
    participant customer_service as Customer / Identity Service
    participant event_bus as Event Backbone
    participant order_service as Order Service
    participant payment_service as Payment Service
    participant fulfilment_service as Fulfilment Service
    web_consumer->>api_gateway: Submit erasure request
    api_gateway->>+customer_service: Route erasure request
    customer_service->>customer_service: Record erasure request
    customer_service->>event_bus: Publish erasure-request event
    par PII deletion across owning services
        event_bus->>order_service: Deliver erasure-request event
        order_service->>order_service: Delete or anonymize owned PII
        order_service->>event_bus: Publish erasure-completed ack
    and
        event_bus->>payment_service: Deliver erasure-request event
        payment_service->>payment_service: Delete or anonymize owned PII
        payment_service->>event_bus: Publish erasure-completed ack
    and
        event_bus->>fulfilment_service: Deliver erasure-request event
        fulfilment_service->>fulfilment_service: Delete or anonymize owned PII
        fulfilment_service->>event_bus: Publish erasure-completed ack
    end
    event_bus->>customer_service: Deliver erasure-completed acks
    customer_service->>customer_service: Finalize profile deletion and mark complete
    customer_service-->>-api_gateway: Erasure accepted